Standard and Poor's Corp said itaffirmed ratings on 500 mln dlrs of Bank of New York Co debtafter the bank set a special LDC loan loss reserve.    Affirmed are the A-plus senior debt rating, the Asubordinated debt, A-1-plus commercial paper and respectiveA-plus and A1-plus ratings on certificates of deposit of Bankof New York and Bank of New York (Delaware).    S and P said the bank's 135 mln dlr addition to its loanloss reserve conservatively addresses LDC exposure. S and Psaid the resulting second quarter loss expected will notsubstantially diminish fundamental earnings strength. Reuter&#3;